title: The Black Coin Old Time Serial (OTS)
description:
If you like the old Serials, which once played in movie houses, one episode per week, usually on Saturday, then this is for you.  But it must be seeded so I will know that it is appreciated.  Show your support by seeding these.  I don't have unlimited bandwidth.  If you vote by your seeding, I will upload more Old Time Serials.

This is the 1939 creation of The Black Coin - Federal agents and smugglers battle it out over lost secret papers. 

Yeah, it's pretty bad but interesting for knowing what used to happen.

Please SEED and remember to tip your waiter
